Package: ttalkR
Type: Package
Title: For download and standard processing of TreeTalker data
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Enrico",
           family = "Tomelleri",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "etomelleri@unibz.it",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6546-6459"))
Description: This package can download and process TreeTalker data. It was designed specifically for the Italian Tree Talker Network but it can be adapted to any other network. The conversion of digital numbers to engineering units are made according to the TT+ User Manual (September 2020).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: tidyr, ggplot2, tidyverse, signal, zoo, suncalc, lubridate, baytrends, RSQLite, RMySQL, dplyr, prospectr
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
